df <- read_csv("data/option_discussed.csv")
df <-
  df %>%
  filter(
    category_remember == 'tissue' |
      category_remember == 'implant' |
      category_remember == 'all'
  ) %>%
  mutate(
    category_remember = category_remember %>% fct_relevel(ref = 'all'),
    category_remember2 = category_remember %>% fct_relevel(ref = 'implant'),
    category_remember3 = category_remember %>% fct_relevel(ref = 'tissue')
  )

library(FSA)

BMI

# bmi is significant
kruskal.test(bmi ~ category_remember, df)
## 
##  Kruskal-Wallis rank sum test
## 
## data:  bmi by category_remember
## Kruskal-Wallis chi-squared = 48, df = 2, p-value = 4e-11
plot_color <- c("#00AFBB", "#E7B800", "#FC4E07")

ggboxplot(
  df,
  x = "category_remember",
  y = "bmi",
  palette = plot_color,
  fill = "category_remember",
  xlab = "Remember options discussed",
  ylab = "BMI"
) + rremove("legend")

dunnTest(bmi ~ category_remember, df)

Normality check

norm_check <- function(x) {
  shapiro.test(x) %>% print()
  hist(x)
  qqnorm(x)
  qqline(x)  
}

norm_check(df$bmi)
## 
##  Shapiro-Wilk normality test
## 
## data:  x
## W = 0.96, p-value = 2e-07
